I '''Yakub Kolas''' ('''Jakub Kołas''' mu naman) ({{lang-be|Яку́б Ко́лас}}, {{OldStyleDate|November 3|1882|October 22}} – Agosto 13, 1956), ing tutung lagiu Kanstantsin Mitskievich (Міцке́віч Канстанці́н Міха́йлавіч) metung yang  [[Belarus]]ian talasulat, Maldang Watas ning [[Byelorussian SSR]] (1926),  ampong kayanib (1928) ampong kaduang-pamuntuk (manibat 1929) ning  [[Belarusian Academy of Sciences]].

Ding kayang obra, i Yakub Kolas kebaluan keng kayang pamakirame kareng maldang Belarusian talapagobra keng gabun.  Iti mayayakit king kayang laigun talapanpan a 'Kolas', kabaldugan a 'balugbug ning butil' keng [[Belarus]]ian. Sinulat yang kasapungul a watas a mikpamagat a ''Kanta ning Makakulung''
<!-- in Russian, ''Песни неволи''-->
(1908) ampong ''Kantang Lugma'' ({{lang-be|Песьні-жальбы}}, 1910), kawatasan ''Ing Bayung Gabun'' ({{lang-be|Новая зямля}}, 1923) ampong ing ''Simon ing Talatugtug'' ({{lang-be|Сымон-музыка}}, 1925), makuyad a salita ampong dramaturgu.  

